text: Athetico Sports Club (), or simply Athetico (), was a women's association football club based in Dbayeh, Lebanon, section of the homonymous sports academy. Founded in 2010 as one of the first women's teams in Lebanon, Athetico were runners up in the 2010 season in the league. They withdrew their team before the 2013 season. == Honours == * Lebanese Women's FA Cup ** Runners-up (1): 2011 == See also == * Lebanese Women's Football League * Women's football in Lebanon * List of women's association football clubs in Lebanon == References == Category:Defunct football clubs in Lebanon Category:Women's football clubs in Lebanon Category:Association football clubs established in 2010 Category:Association football clubs disestablished in 2013
